<img src="http://imgs.xkcd.com/comics/valentine_dilemma.png" title="The worst resolution to the Valentine Prisoner&#39;s Dilemma when YOU decide not to give your partner a present but your PARTNER decides to testify against you in the armed robbery case." alt="Valentine Dilemma" />
</div>
